A lot of twists and deaths. I feel like: This movie had some of the best and worst moments in Star Wars history. There are obvious moments where you're hyped up on adrenaline because what's occurring in front of you is so cool and other moments where you sit back and ask \"What just happened?\" It's not better than Episode V\, but it's not abysmal. There is a good bit of juvenile humor but it's not important.
